<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich VI. Reuß von Plauen</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen Andreas Steinpach mit, dass dieser das angedeutete Einlenken verbriefen soll.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_257" id="128r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_257_r1l2"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Plauwen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_257_r1l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Steinpach des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l4"><expan>Jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Nu hat er vaſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l5">vnd <expan>ſwerlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vns getan / als ewr edel leıcht <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol wais </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l6">Doch ew cʒü eren vnd gevallnüʒʒ / Wer es daʒ er vns abnemen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l7">Peſſerung tün wolt 
<del rend="strikethrough">nach rate </del> / vnd daʒ Jr vns das an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l8"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchribt</expan> / . Nach dem vnd Jr vns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> verſchribt / So <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l9">vvir ew 
<del rend="strikethrough">ein cʒeite <expan>benenne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darynne Jr einen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">frıd <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> möchte / vnd köm er cʒü teydingen / was vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen tun <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir ew lıeber <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>yemand<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">volgen / . </del> darauf <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein antwurt <expan>verſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Vnd wo vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l13"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lıeb vnd dienſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_257_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georij / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_257" id="128r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü Plauwen
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Steinpach des <expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. Nu hat er vast und
                                <expan>swerlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns getan, als ewr edel leicht
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol wais, doch ew czü eren und
                        gevallnüzz wer es, daz er uns abnemen und pesserung tün wolt und daz ir uns
                        das an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan>, nach dem und ir uns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> verschribt, so
                            <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew darauf
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein antwurt
                            <expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb und dienst
                                <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
